Subject: [PATCH] drm/i915/gt: Restore clear-residual mitigations for Ivybridge, Baytrail
Git-commit: 09aa9e45863e9e25dfbf350bae89fc3c2964482c
Patch-mainline: v5.11-rc4
No-fix: 008ead6ef8f588a8c832adfe9db201d9be5fd410
